<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A9B06010" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
A-Pillar Outer Panel, Front Door Hinge Reinforcement and Dash Side Panel Removal and Installation
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
The figure below shows condition where following parts are removed.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Front fender 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9A06005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Hood lock member, lamp support member and lamp support brace 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B06001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Cowl side outer member 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B06005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Dash side front panel with cowl top side front panel 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B06006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0040.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "56.208mm" ver = "01" gw = "227" gh = "143"/>
</figure>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9B06010001">
<title>
General Notes
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Welding method and number of welding points are the same on both sides. This repair instruction shows procedure for left side.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Part filled with foamed material is included in parts of this repair. Therefore, repair referring to 
<intxref refid = "AENBP70A9B06022">Foamed Material Filling Area Repair</intxref>
 for precautions and repair procedure.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
The dimensions shown in the figure are reference values when cutting replacement part placed on top of existing part. Determine most appropriate cutting (or joint) line considering both size of replacement part and condition of existing part.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9B06010002">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Mark at the shown position and cut A-pillar outer panel.
</ptxt>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
You may accidentally cut the parts under the A-pillar outer panel or the parts under the side sill outer panel when cutting the A-pillar outer panel.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Take sufficient care not to damage the parts under the A-pillar outer panel or the parts under the side sill outer panel when cutting the A-pillar outer panel.
</ptxt>
</attention4>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Bend open metal tab (arrow) and remove A-pillar outer panel.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0068.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "210.274mm" ver = "06" gw = "497" gh = "580"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots and remove front door hinge reinforcement, door hinge retainer and front door hinge upper reinforcement.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0041.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "153.828mm" ver = "07" gw = "406" gh = "420"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "5.878in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
When heating around foamed material application portion to detach foamed material, be sure that temperature of said portion does not reach 170 &#176;C (338 &#176;F).
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots and remove dash panel side reinforcement.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0042.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "146.437mm" ver = "01" gw = "486" gh = "399"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Unscrew 3 bolts and remove dash side panel.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0069.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "140.497mm" ver = "06" gw = "491" gh = "382"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "5.631in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Grind welding spots using belt sander, if necessary.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
When heating around sealer application portion to detach body sealer, be sure that temperature of said portion does not reach 170 &#176;C (338 &#176;F).
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9B06010003">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Before conducting any weld, check installation position and condition for installation part(s). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B04006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B04007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Proceed repair while taking into consideration installation of parts that affect appearance. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B04003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install dash side panel.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct resistance spot weld and plug weld.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Tighten 3 bolts to specified torque.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0070.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "143.545mm" ver = "02" gw = "491" gh = "390"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.789in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MATORQUE-A" width = "8.011mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
10 N&#183;m (1.0 kgf-m, 7.5 lbf-ft)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install dash panel side reinforcement.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct resistance spot weld and plug weld.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0044.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "146.437mm" ver = "02" gw = "486" gh = "399"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install door hinge retainer and front door hinge upper reinforcement.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct resistance spot weld or plug weld.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0045.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "121.213mm" ver = "04" gw = "204" gh = "327"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Repair foamed material. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9B06022"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0046.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "162.701mm" ver = "03" gw = "485" gh = "445"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "8" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.745in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.730in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "1.215in"/>
<colspec colnum = "7" colname = "7" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "8" colname = "8" colwidth = "1.196in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Foamed material
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Front door hinge reinforcement
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Dash side panel
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "7" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
4.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "8" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Baffle plate
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install front door hinge reinforcement.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct plug weld.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0047.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "153.828mm" ver = "05" gw = "406" gh = "420"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install new A-pillar outer panel to vehicle body and cut in stacked condition.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install A-pillar outer panel.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct resistance spot weld and plug weld.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct continuous weld.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply anticorrosion wax to back side of continuous weld part.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Bend in metal tab (arrow) of A-pillar outer panel.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0071.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "231.685mm" ver = "06" gw = "497" gh = "640"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.472in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.706in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Conduct resistance spot weld as three panel thickness.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
